title: Arbor Women's SS12 Apparel Collection
description:
The SS12 women's line explores more feminine fabrics and silhouettes including new beautiful modal based tops and dresses. As always the collection is made exclusively from environmentally responsible fabrics.

http://arborcollective.com/apparel/
